{"tid":2402414,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一個好識調教眼鏡既師傅係造福近視既人類","createTime":"2021-02-10T11:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T01:17:30.000Z","uid":203199,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f1e9a91e5f7a039b348b361908c7c68e2d932e","tid":2402414,"uid":203199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"本身有高低耳，但仲要對眼鏡既平衡感要求特別高，配過好多眼鏡都唔岩心水，直到遇上一位經驗超勁既眼鏡師，真係跟住你面型調教，三兩下手勢搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a688fc74c8fee04ab548eecaec25fa5ac3dce9e7","tid":2402414,"uid":65031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"我見啲師傅係調番正嗰眼鏡<br />\n而唔係好似你嗰師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b098e43b7999c0f35f7d175d68368d3e455a731","tid":2402414,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bbba1880fe7b2a23d01293cec8fcceaffc95f4","tid":2402414,"uid":36877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遇唔到<br />\n請問你個位係邊㗎"},{"pid":"cfdd98d1d0c7dfb4f1948e52aeb05a52d2d23efb","tid":2402414,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2dfa139ee6f773369bd41ca38b3506f0e8d61d74","tid":2402414,"uid":59501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"你個師傅係邊度？<br />\n我都有高低耳<br />\n戴一陣隻眼就好攰好唔舒服<br />\n感覺要好用神睇野<br />\n唔知係咪眼距唔啱定點<br />\n整過幾次都係咁<br />\ndllm仲戴到對眼好似搞到有少少分開射喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但反而戴con戴十幾個鐘都乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac75c07af79557141231297fed8146f48e23ad9","tid":2402414,"uid":203199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"係Jins，九龍塘，一位老師傅，當初諗住指佢點樣調，跟住佢講左句，我教左30年眼鏡，等我睇下就知，之後就勁舒服"},{"pid":"bdc9885a0bb3629da8cd4302df0d4093a6d4b24f","tid":2402414,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:10:28.000Z","msg":"有冇拎佢電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺一個好嘅調眼鏡師傅好緊要"},{"pid":"089a5269bbc12ef53230aa4f63d6e0cae3dfe159","tid":2402414,"uid":203199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdc9885a0bb3629da8cd4302df0d4093a6d4b24f","tid":2402414,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:10:28.000Z","msg":"有冇拎佢電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺一個好嘅調眼鏡師傅好緊要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"yes，真心緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫Tony，佢好勁抽"},{"pid":"7838db6b3e82d0b9376ba716fa3d73cad1ddad53","tid":2402414,"uid":203199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"以後眼鏡有咩問題一定搵佢，再配都係搵佢"},{"pid":"19a6932b9eb66b739042cefac8518e8b8aa11d56","tid":2402414,"uid":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac75c07af79557141231297fed8146f48e23ad9","tid":2402414,"uid":203199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"係Jins，九龍塘，一位老師傅，當初諗住指佢點樣調，跟住佢講左句，我教左30年眼鏡，等我睇下就知，之後就勁舒服"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f33f4776a27d016b0fdbdbabc05986d9c6a78b","tid":2402414,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a6932b9eb66b739042cefac8518e8b8aa11d56","tid":2402414,"uid":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac75c07af79557141231297fed8146f48e23ad9","tid":2402414,"uid":203199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"係Jins，九龍塘，一位老